    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Do we want to allow BurnableTokens to be burned if sended to 0 address?\r\nAlso, may be it is useful to burn tokens sended to the token address. This'll allow simple burning tokens from any wallet which supports ERC20.\r\nAlso, may be it is usefull to allow token holders to be rewarded for burning. So we may end up with smth like this: https://github.com/MATREXA/MTRX-Contract/blob/master/BurnableToken.sol\r\n",
