    "body": "I think we should keep the semantics of `transfer` as they are. I wouldn't expect a token to be burnable through a standard ERC20 wallet.\r\n\r\nThe reward mechanism is interesting! Quite rare, though. I don't think most tokens will find use in something like it.\r\n\r\nClosing since it was fixed by #341!",
